<item>
            <title>[OAK-695] TypeEditor must not check hidden nodes</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/OAK-695</link>
                <project id="12313221" key="OAK">Jackrabbit Oak</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Hidden nodes like those created by the p2 index are not JCR nodes and must not be checked by the TypeValidator.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I encountered this issue when running tests with the new MongoMK, but I&apos;m wondering why we don&apos;t see this more often...&lt;/p&gt;</description>
